## 8. Activation Milestones (Product-Led Growth Playbook)

### The "Aha Moment" for Winzinvest

The moment a user realizes the value. For Winzinvest, this is likely:

> **"First time the system places a trade automatically and it works"**

Or more specifically:

> **"First time the system prevents them from taking a bad trade"**

**Secondary aha moments:**
- First covered call auto-rolled at 80% profit
- First time drawdown tier cuts position sizes (saves them from bigger loss)
- First winning trade they didn't have to watch

### Time-to-Value Ladder

Get users to aha moment as fast as possible:

| Milestone | Target Time | What Happens |
|---|---|---|
| Account connected | Day 0 | Link IBKR API, see live positions |
| First signal seen | Day 1 | Pre-market screener runs, dashboard shows candidates |
| First automated trade | Day 3 | System places order, user sees fill notification |
| First stop adjustment | Day 4 | Trailing stop moves up, locking in gain |
| First options roll | Week 2 | Covered call hits 80% decay, auto-rolled |

**Onboarding goal:** Get to "first automated trade" within 72 hours of signup.

